{"lemma":"خاناتٌ","slug":"خاناتٌ","root":"خ.ن.ن","root_slug":"خ-ن-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ن-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11764"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"space into which a physical object is fitted, cubbyhole"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"space into which data is entered, field, column, box, and the like"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the entry itself, its informational content"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the rank of such an entry"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the place in a numeral string of multiple digits (German Stelle)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Classical Persian خَانَه (xāna, “house”), or from خَان (ḵān, “caravanserai”) + ـَة (-a) in so far as a caravanserai offered a space to fit the camel or horse in."},"ipa":["/xaː.na/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11764","headword_ar":"خَانَهُ","root":"xwn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxuwnuhu","text_ar":"يَخُونُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaAnapN","text_ar":"خِيَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawonN","text_ar":"خَوْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaAnapN","text_ar":"مَخَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAnapN","text_ar":"خَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAy^inapN","text_ar":"خَايِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilapN","text_ar":"فَاعِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAgiyapN","text_ar":"لَاغِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AxtAnhu","text_ar":"اختانهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was unfaithful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted unfaithfully, to the confidence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trust, that he reposed in him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was treache rous, perfidious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unfaithful, to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted treacherously, perfidiously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unfaithfully, towards him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaAnapN","text_ar":"خِيَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amaAnapN","text_ar":"اَمَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and does not relate only to property, but also to other things: (Mgh:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"neglecting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"failing in,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amaAnapN","text_ar":"اَمَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trustiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faithfulness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (El-Harállee, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nifaAqN","text_ar":"نِفَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", except that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xyAnp","text_ar":"خيانة"},{"kind":"text","text":"regards a compact or covenant or the like, and trustiness, or faith fulness, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nfAq","text_ar":"نفاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"regards religion; so that the former is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acting contrary to what is right, by breaking a compact"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covenant"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er Rághib, TA:) but [it is said that] the primary signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawonN","text_ar":"خَوْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making to suffer loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diminution;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAy^in","text_ar":"خَايِن"},{"kind":"text","text":"makes the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxuwn","text_ar":"مَخُون"},{"kind":"text","text":"to suffer loss, or diminution, of something. (TA.) Hence, in the Kur [ii. 183],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kunotumo","text_ar":"كُنْتُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofusakumo","text_ar":"اَنْفُسَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxotaAnuwna","text_ar":"تَخْتَانُونَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye used to act unfaith fully to yourselves"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye used to act un faithfully, one to another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye used to act wrongfully to yourselves:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotiyaAnN","text_ar":"اِخْتِيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a more intensive signification than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaAnapN","text_ar":"خِيَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAn AlEahoda","text_ar":"خان العَهْدَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke the compact"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covenant"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taquwlu Aln~iEomapu","text_ar":"تَقُولُ النِّعْمَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kufirotu walamo A^u$okaro wataquwlu AlA^amaAnapu xunotu walamo A^uHofaZo","text_ar":"كُفِرْتُ وَلَمْ اُشْكَرْ وَتَقُولُ الاَمَانَةُ خُنْتُ وَلَمْ اُحْفَظْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The benefit says, I have been disacknowledged, and have not been requited with thankfulness; and the trust says, I have been betrayed, and have not been faithfully kept"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: the verb ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xunotu","text_ar":"خُنْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] being here of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEilotu","text_ar":"فُعِلْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a verb of which the agent is not named. (Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAnahu AlEahoda","text_ar":"خَانَهُ العَهْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlEahodi","text_ar":"فِى العَهْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAnhu AlA^amaAnapa","text_ar":"خانهُ الاَمَانَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawonN","text_ar":"خَوْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaAnapN","text_ar":"خِيَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaAnapN","text_ar":"مَخَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was unfaithful to him in respect of the compact"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covenant"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the trust."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAn sayofuhu","text_ar":"خان سَيْفُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His sword was unfaithful;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"failed of taking ef fect upon the thing struck with it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) A cer tain person, being asked respecting the sword, said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axuwka wa rub~amaA xaAnaka","text_ar":"اَخُوكَ وَ رُبَّمَا خَانَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  [It is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy brother, but sometimes it is unfaithful to thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAnatohu rijolaAhu","text_ar":"خَانَتْهُ رِجْلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His two legs were unfaithful to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was unable to walk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAn Ald~alowa Alr~i$aA='u","text_ar":"خان الدَّلْوَ الرِّشَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The well-rope broke off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be came severed, from the bucket."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAnhu Ald~ahoru","text_ar":"خانهُ الدَّهْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawonN","text_ar":"خَوْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txw~nhu","text_ar":"تخوّنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time altered his state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from softness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easiness, to hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to evil;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA;) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aEiymu","text_ar":"النَّعِيمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enjoyment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: and of everything that has altered thy state, or condition, [for the worse,] one says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxaw~anaka","text_ar":"تَخَوَّنَكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Mgh","Msb","T","TA"]}]}}